501
00:34:29,083 --> 00:34:32,211
All right, honey.
When we get up we'll listen to it again.

502
00:34:32,386 --> 00:34:35,412
Okay, that's a good idea.

503
00:34:35,590 --> 00:34:37,080
Night, darling.

504
00:34:37,258 --> 00:34:39,021
Night.

505
