00:39:44,865 --> 00:39:45,957
Dixie wants me to sing it.

591
00:39:46,133 --> 00:39:48,294
"Your Words And My Music"
is one song you'll never sing.

592
00:39:48,469 --> 00:39:49,561
- Yes, I will.
- You won't.

